name: __EEvaluatorMode
doc: Determines the behavior this node will use when updating and evaluating.

EM_Standard: DataSource is ticked and evaluated every frame.
EM_Freeze: DataSource is never ticked and only evaluated on the first frame. Every frame after uses the cached pose from the first frame.
EM_DelayedFreeze: DataSource is ticked and evaluated for a given number of frames, then freezes after and uses the cached pose for future frames.
